reviewText: Great movies and a great price!!
DVD came quickly and am pleased w/this purchase.  I like the British DVD's.  I would recommend this DVD.
Becoming Jane was fantastic!  Absolutely loved it. Now I need to view the other two movies.  Scenery, acting, storyline were all superb.  What a great way to spend some down time.
Good films, good quality dvd, promptly delivered.
